{
  "texts": [
    "A reviewer using a mixed-based heuristic stopping strategy would decide to stop the abstract screening after classifying a certain percentage of all the abstracts included in an abstract collection and classifying a certain percentage of consecutive abstracts as irrelevant.",
    "Table 6 presents the sensitivity and specificity of the nine mixed-based heuristic stopping criteria evaluated in this study (labeled as groups A to I).",
